 It is also argued by appellant that the first notice was insufficient. In the case of 
}
{\b0 \cf22 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://1.next.westlaw.com/Link/RelatedInformation/Flag?documentGuid=I27ede0a7f7e611d983e7e9deff98dc6f&transitionType=InlineKeyCiteFlags&originationContext=docHeaderFlag&Rank=0&ppcid=ea419c1c2e8e4ee19b2740f47a63fcc2&contextData=(sc.UserEnteredCitation)" }{\fldrslt 
