{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1919002176&pubNum=660&originatingDoc=Icc0564a5f88311d99439b076ef9ec4de&refType=RP&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.UserEnteredCitation)" }{\fldrslt 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul1 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
180 Pac. 873,
